<L>__{interior airport hangar later}
<A>__{the plane has been brought into a hangar where it's being taken apart like a car stripped by thieves. inside the cabin, seats are removed and inspected, carpeting pulled up, panels unscrewed, lavatories dismantled. downstairs ana and frank's mother, guarded, can hear trupo and his detectives, upstairs, ransacking a bedroom. upstairs the siu detectives pull open drawers, throw clothes from the closets. trupo picks up an invitation to a united nations ball, tosses it down again. finds a safety deposit box key in a sock drawer, puts it in his pocket. the engines and landing gear are disassembled, the tires opened up and searched. a nozzle plunges into a toilet and pumps out the contents into barrels detectives fish through with gloved hands }
